{"article_id":"Ze2TE3Prsllqbh2l","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump slammed Iran Friday ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"calling the country a `` menace ''","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"and announced new sanctions against its regime","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"-- but did not take action","depth":3},{"id":4,"text":"to alter the Obama-era nuclear deal","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"that he has denounced since his presidential campaign .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Interested in Iran ?","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"Add Iran as an interest","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"to stay up to date on the latest Iran news , video , and analysis from .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Add Interest","depth":3},{"id":10,"text":"The deal ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"is no longer in the national security interest of the United States .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"This decision ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"which has been referred to as \" decertification , \"","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"is a shift in official position .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"It is a significant declaration","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that leaves the nuclear agreement in place ,","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"but puts Congress in charge","depth":12},{"id":19,"text":"of whether or not to follow up with action","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"-- triggering a 60-day window","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"for lawmakers","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"to re-impose sanctions against Iran","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"that were suspended in 2015 as part of the agreement .","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"Trump outlined three steps as part of America 's path forward :","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"to counter `` destabilizing activity '' in the Middle East ,","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"impose new sanctions on non-nuclear aspects of the regime","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"and address the country 's nuclear ambitions .","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"`` Our policy is based on clear assessment of Iranian dictatorship , its sponsorship of terrorism and its continuing aggression in the Middle East and all around the world , ''","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"While the president portrayed the decision","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"as having originated with his administration ,","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"he acknowledged","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that Congress holds the key to the deal 's future .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"`` I am directing my administration to work closely with Congress and our allies","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"to address the deal 's many serious flaws","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"so that the Iranian regime can never threaten the world with nuclear weapons , ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Tehran and world powers in July 2015 crafted a deal","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"that eased sanctions on Iran in exchange for stepped-up international monitoring of its nuclear development activities .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"The agreement reduced the amount of nuclear fuel","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Iran can keep","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and extended the `` breakout time ''","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"needed for Iran to create a single bomb .","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Some of Iran 's facilities are now also subject to constant monitoring ,","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"with others subject to inspections after a waiting period .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"The president accused Iran of `` not living up to the spirit of the deal , ''","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"while the U.S. abides by its promises ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"despite top officials on his national security team ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"including Defense Secretary James Mattis ,","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"Iran has technically complied with its restrictions .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"The International Atomic Energy Association ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"tasked with validating Iran 's adherence to the agreement ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"released a statement Friday","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"further confirming the country 's compliance .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"`` At present , Iran is subject to the world 's most robust nuclear verification regime , ''","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"the IAEA said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"Trump 's remarks ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"while not alleging a specific violation of the nuclear-related terms ,","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"singled out the `` Iranian regime '' for `` continu [ ing ]","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"to fuel conflict , terror , and turmoil throughout the Middle East and beyond . ''","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Iranian President Hassan Rouhani defended his country 's participation in the deal Friday after Trump 's speech","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"and attacked the decision ,","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that the U.S. was `` completely alone '' in its policy toward Iran .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"He added","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"that Iran would not hesitate to respond","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"if the deal 's other parties `` do not stay loyal . ''","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Rouhani further characterized Iran ' s missile program as purely defensive in nature and necessary in the face of U.S. aggression .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"\" We always tried to produce weapons ourselves , \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"\" And from now on we will redouble that effort ...","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"to defend ourselves . \"","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"In a series of tweets Friday afternoon , Iran 's Foreign Minister Javad Zarif portrayed Trump as kowtowing to external interests ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"and describing the U.S. president 's words as `` rogue . '' Everyone knew","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"Trump ' s friendship was for sale to the highest bidder .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"We now know","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"that his geography is too .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"2/ - Javad Zarif","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"( @ JZarif )","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"October 13 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"Trump also announced sanctions Friday on Iran 's Revolutionary Guard Corps ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"whom he accused of providing assistance to terrorist groups .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"He encouraged U.S. allies to take action","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"to counter the group 's efforts","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"`` including thorough sanctions outside the Iran deal","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"that target the regime 's ballistic missile program in support for terrorism and all of its destructive activities ,","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"of which there are many . ''","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"Though Trump did not go so far as to end the nuclear deal ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"he told reporters on the White House South Lawn after his speech","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"that his prior threat","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"to `` rip it up ''","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"was still a possibility .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"`` I may do that .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"I may do that , ''","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"`` The deal is terrible .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"So what we 've done is , through the certification process , we 'll have Congress take a look at it","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"and I may very well do that .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"But I like a two-step process much better . ''","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Republicans critical of the initial deal have urged the administration to enforce it .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"Sen. John McCain , R-Ariz. said in a statement Friday","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"that he agrees with Trump","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"that the deal does n't benefit U.S. interests ,","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"but that he is interested in approving ,","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"rather than ending , it .","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"`` I look forward to working with my colleagues in Congress on additional legislation","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"to increase sanctions and other pressure","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"to hold Iran accountable for its broader destructive behavior in the region , ''","depth":15},{"id":110,"text":"McCain said in the statement .","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"`` I am also eager to collaborate with our partners and allies","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"to revisit the most problematic provisions of the nuclear deal ,","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"and support a unified , forceful international front in the event","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"that Iran materially breaches the terms of the agreement . ''","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"On Wednesday , House Foreign Affairs Committee Chairman Ed Royce , R-Calif. said in a hearing","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":117,"text":"while he felt","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"the deal was `` flawed , ''","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"he believed","depth":14},{"id":120,"text":"the U.S. `` must now enforce the hell out of it . ''","depth":14},{"id":121,"text":"\" Let ' s work with allies","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"to make certain","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"that international inspectors have better access to possible nuclear sites ,","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"and we should address the fundamental sunset shortcoming ,","depth":13},{"id":125,"text":"as our allies have recognized , ''","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"said Royce .","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"Even Sen. Tom Cotton , R-Ark. , one of the most vocal critics of the Iran deal and supporters of decertification , has recommended","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"holding off on \" snapping back , \"","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"or restoring immediately , the nuclear sanctions","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"lifted as part of the deal .","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"He called the move a \" backward-looking step \"","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"and said","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"Congress should instead impose new ballistic sanctions","depth":14},{"id":134,"text":"and lift some of the Iran agreement ' s sunset provisions","depth":15},{"id":135,"text":"which allow some regulatory measures to expire after certain periods .","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"The goal with such actions ,","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"according to Cotton ,","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"would be to bring Iran back to the negotiating table","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"to strengthen the original deal .","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"But some Obama-era officials","depth":15},{"id":141,"text":"who worked on the agreement","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"said","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"that hope was unrealistic .","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"\" I would love to see Iran come back to the table ,","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"apologizes for everything","depth":16},{"id":146,"text":"and agree to all of our demands , \"","depth":16},{"id":147,"text":"Philip Gordon , White House coordinator for the Middle East during the Iran negotiations , told .","depth":14},{"id":148,"text":"But he called such a notion a \" fantasy . \"","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"Former Secretary of State John Kerry , a signatory to the agreement","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"who personally engaged in the final negotiations ,","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"released a highly critical statement after Trump 's speech Friday .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"Kerry called Trump 's decision a `` dangerous ''","depth":15},{"id":153,"text":"on that `` polluted the negotiating waters , ''","depth":15},{"id":154,"text":"and expressed bewilderment","depth":15},{"id":155,"text":"at why the president would not recognize Iran 's adherence to the terms .","depth":15},{"id":156,"text":"He called on Congress to follow through","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"in maintaining the spirit of the deal .","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"`` Our allies and our Congress must now act as the only adults","depth":16},{"id":159,"text":"left in the room","depth":16},{"id":160,"text":"with the power","depth":16},{"id":161,"text":"to protect our national interests , ''","depth":16},{"id":162,"text":"the statement read , in part ,","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"adding ,","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"`` I ca n't think of a more important moment than this one","depth":15},{"id":165,"text":"where cooler , wiser voices have had a bigger responsibility","depth":16},{"id":166,"text":"to put a policy back on track . ''","depth":16},{"id":167,"text":"It 's all hands on deck","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"standing up to President Trumps 's dangerous decision on Iran .","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"Here 's my statement .","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"pic.twitter.com/VsTBwrqBZQ","depth":14},{"id":171,"text":"- John Kerry","depth":14},{"id":172,"text":"( @ JohnKerry )","depth":14},{"id":173,"text":"October 13 , 2017","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"Sen. Bob Corker , R-Tenn. , the chairman of the Senate Foreign Relations Committee","depth":11},{"id":175,"text":"who led the charge against the bill","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"and wrote a law","depth":13},{"id":177,"text":"forcing congressional oversight of the Iran agreement ,","depth":13},{"id":178,"text":"has also expressed skepticism","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"that decertifying the deal is the right decision .","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"\" You can only tear these things up one time .","depth":10},{"id":181,"text":"It might feel good for a second ,","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"but one of the things","depth":15},{"id":183,"text":"that 's important for us","depth":15},{"id":184,"text":"is to keep our allies with us , \"","depth":14},{"id":185,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":186,"text":"referring to the other signatories of the Iran deal","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"which include China and Russia as well as the European Union .","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"While many of the parties to the deal spoke out against Trump 's stance ,","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"the president found supporters in a pair of regional allies","depth":13},{"id":190,"text":"who were not signatories to the agreement :","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"the United Arab Emirates and Saudi Arabia .","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"The latter described the U.S. 's strategy Friday as `` resolute '' and a `` clear-eyed vision . ''","depth":13},{"id":193,"text":"Both the UAE and Saudi Arabia are considered regional rivals of Iran","depth":11},{"id":194,"text":"and have made overtures","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"to work towards a closer relationship with the Trump administration","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"since the president 's inauguration in January .","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"Each country expressed public support for the nuclear deal upon its signing ,","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"despite reservations .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":397,"left":204,"right":396,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":201,"right":203,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":0,"right":200,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":3,"right":202,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":396,"left":207,"right":395,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":207,"left":206,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":206,"left":6,"right":205,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":205,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":395,"left":242,"right":394,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":234